---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Our Services"
description: "Pole barns, garages, horse barns, barndominiums, and steel buildings. See the full range of services CNO Pole Barns builds across southeast Michigan and get a free estimate."
permalink: /services/
---

{# ========== SERVICES INDEX ========== #}

<header class="ohero noimg slim">
  <div class="wrap"><div class="ohero-inner stagger">
    <span class="lab">What We Build</span>
    <h1>Our Services</h1>
    <p class="lead">Pole barns, garages, horse barns, barndominiums, and steel buildings. Pick a service below to see project photos and details, or call us if you are not sure what you need.</p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-green">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    </div>
  </div></div>
</header>

<section class="blk"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="head reveal"><h2>Everything we build</h2><p>Pick a service to see project photos, details, and answers to common questions.</p></div>
  <div class="svc stagger">
    {% for service in collections.services %}
    <a class="card" href="{{ service.url }}">
      <div class="im"><img src="{{ service.data.image }}" alt="{{ service.data.title }}"></div>
      <div class="bd">
        <h3>{{ service.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ service.data.subtitle }}</p>
        <span class="lk">Learn more &rarr;</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</div></section>

<section class="blk cta"><div class="wrap"><div class="box reveal">
  <h2>Not sure what you need?</h2>
  <p>Tell us about your project and we will recommend the right building. Free estimates, no pressure.</p>
  <div class="row">
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-dark">Get a Free Estimate</a>
    <a href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}" class="btn btn-ghost" style="border-color:rgba(13,36,21,.3);color:#0d2415">Call {{ site.phone }}</a>
  </div>
</div></div></section>
